const colors = {
  transparent: 'transparent',
  labelColor: '#767676',
  inactiveField: '#f2f2f2',
  inactiveButton: '#b7dbdd',
  inactiveIcon: '#EBEBEB',
  primaryHover: '#006b70',
  secondary: '#ff5b60',
  secondaryHover: '#FF282F',
  yellow: '#fdb32a',
  yellowHover: '#F29E02',
  borderColor: '#dadada',
  black: '#000000',
  white: '#ffffff',
  primary: '#1A73E8',
  headingColor: '#0f2137',
  quoteText: '#343d48',
  textColor: 'rgba(52, 61, 72, 0.8)',
  linkColor: '#2b9eff',
};

export default colors;
